Popular Nigerian cross-dresser and internet personality, Okuneye Idris, widely known as Bobrisky, is reported to be on the run after police raided a nude party organised by him in Lekki area of Lagos. Bobrisky put up the party in celebration of his 28th birthday, but it was disrupted by the Nigeria Police, who invaded the place and dispersed guests. Photos and a video of the event centre showed several police vehicles stationed around the venue. However, the cross-dresser, who recently revealed that he has cut off his penis was said to had left his event centre before the police stormed the place.  No one has heard from him since then and the police has not also stated why the event was stopped and who ordered them to do so. Five people were said to have been arrested, according to the Sun. The birthday party was held at The Pearl Gardens in Lekki, Lagos. Recall that the Federal Government through the Director-General of the National Council for Arts and Culture, Otunba Olusegub had threatened to deal with Bobrisky. He said, “Bobrisky is a national disgrace. He started by selling and using bleaching creams, now, he has grown boobs, bums and hips.”  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.